                            Dockchain is a platform for  Academic certificate and identity verification.If a person wants to verify the  originality of the certificate the person need to authenticate the certificate from the certificate issuing
                            authority. The person takes much time for certificate verification to check the originality of the certificate. The overall certificate verification process
